metadata.name: Thismansbrand X Chris Arvan #11
metadata.description:
Western Denim color blocked top with rhinestones and faux leather brocade and denim strapping on back. Color blocked denim pant with faux leather, rhinestones and brocade detail.

The first collector of this NFT will receive the entire outfit including accessories (excluding jewelry).

Designer - Marc Littlejohn | Artwork & Photography by Chris Arvan
